      "actionDate": "2025-02-26",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Entrepreneurs with Disabilities Reporting Act of 2025</strong></p><p>This bill requires the Small Business Administration to assess and report on the challenges that entrepreneurs with a disability encounter in starting and operating a business, including any recommendations for legislative actions to address those challenges.</p>",
